def compare_versions(ver1,ver2):
    v1 = list(map(int, ver1.split('.')))
    v2 = list(map(int, ver2.split('.')))
    
    len_v1 = len(v1)
    len_v2 = len(v2)
    
    max_len = max(len_v1, len_v2)
    
    v1 += [0] * (max_len - len_v1)
    v2 += [0] * (max_len - len_v2)
    
    for i in range(max_len):
        if v1[i] > v2[i]:
            return True
        elif v1[i] < v2[i]:
            return False
            
    return True
